@startuml Browsing Campgrounds Diagram

title Campground Features Flow

actor User
participant "Web App" as App
participant "Campground Service" as Camp
participant "Favorite Service" as Fav

User -> App: Open campgrounds page
App -> Camp: Fetch campgrounds list
Camp --> App: Return campgrounds list
App --> User: Display campgrounds

User -> App: Mark campground as favorite
App -> Fav: Add to favorites
Fav --> App: Favorite added
App --> User: Confirmation

User -> App: Check availability
App -> Camp: Get availability details
Camp --> App: Return availability
App --> User: Display availability

@enduml